<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>
	<GameConditionDef>
		<defName>NY_ForgingDragon_HotRain</defName>
		<conditionClass>ForgingDragon.GameCondition_DragonWeather</conditionClass>
		<label>闷热雨季</label>
		<description>雨时刻不停地下着，伴随着气温的升高，整个世界变得潮湿闷热，令人窒息。</description>
		<endMessage>热浪退去，雨水停息，雨季结束了。</endMessage>
		<letterText>热空气与水汽开始在这片土地上方汇聚，一场漫长的雨季即将到来，希望天上落下的不会是开水。</letterText>
		<letterDef>NegativeEvent</letterDef>
		<canBePermanent>true</canBePermanent>
		<weatherDef>Rain</weatherDef><!--这里填指定天气-->
		<temperatureOffset>20</temperatureOffset><!--这里填变化的温度,不用就填0-->
		<exclusiveConditions>
			<li>NY_ForgingDragon_Drought</li>
			<li>NY_ForgingDragon_ColdSnap</li>
			<li>NY_ForgingDragon_ColdFreeze</li>
		</exclusiveConditions>
	</GameConditionDef>

	<GameConditionDef>
		<defName>NY_ForgingDragon_Drought</defName>
		<conditionClass>ForgingDragon.GameCondition_Drought</conditionClass>
		<label>干旱</label>
		<description>干燥的空气正在掠走本就稀少的水分，一切事物仿佛都在干枯，植物也纷纷死去。</description>
		<endMessage>干旱迎来终结，只要再来一场大雨，这片土地就能焕发生机。</endMessage>
		<letterText>气温逐渐升高，远方吹来的热风中不带有一丝水汽，愈发干燥的土壤预示着某种灾难的到来。</letterText>
		<letterDef>NegativeEvent</letterDef>
		<canBePermanent>true</canBePermanent>
		<allowUnderground>false</allowUnderground>
		<pennedAnimalsSeekShelter>true</pennedAnimalsSeekShelter>
		<weatherDef>NY_DroughtClear</weatherDef>
		<temperatureOffset>20</temperatureOffset>
		<exclusiveConditions>
			<li>NY_ForgingDragon_HotRain</li>
			<li>NY_ForgingDragon_ColdSnap</li>
			<li>NY_ForgingDragon_ColdFreeze</li>
		</exclusiveConditions>
	</GameConditionDef>

	<GameConditionDef>
		<defName>NY_ForgingDragon_ColdSnap</defName>
		<conditionClass>ForgingDragon.GameCondition_DragonWeather</conditionClass>
		<label>平流寒害</label>
		<description>阴冷与风寒笼罩着这片土地，灰暗的天空与怪异的风声令人心生绝望。</description>
		<endMessage>寒风平息，天气开始回暖。</endMessage>
		<letterText>强冷空气正在不断涌入这片土地，天空开始变得阴沉。</letterText>
		<letterDef>NegativeEvent</letterDef>
		<canBePermanent>true</canBePermanent>
		<allowUnderground>false</allowUnderground>
		<weatherDef>NY_ColdWindy</weatherDef>
		<temperatureOffset>-20</temperatureOffset>
		<exclusiveConditions>
			<li>HeatWave</li>
			<li>NY_ForgingDragon_HotRain</li>
			<li>NY_ForgingDragon_Drought</li>
		</exclusiveConditions>
	</GameConditionDef>

	<GameConditionDef>
		<defName>NY_ForgingDragon_ColdFreeze</defName>
		<conditionClass>ForgingDragon.GameCondition_DragonWeather</conditionClass>
		<label>急性霜冻</label>
		<description>降温，没有尽头的降温，严寒裹挟着大雪吞没了整个世界，在一夜之间铸就一座冰霜的地狱。</description>
		<endMessage>冰雪终会融化，顽强的生命总能战胜自然的恶意。</endMessage>
		<letterText>气温急速下降，厚重的阴云缓慢压来，死亡已经磨好了冰霜的镰，渴望着收割生命。</letterText>
		<letterDef>NegativeEvent</letterDef>
		<canBePermanent>true</canBePermanent>
		<allowUnderground>false</allowUnderground>
		<pennedAnimalsSeekShelter>true</pennedAnimalsSeekShelter>
		<weatherDef>SnowHard</weatherDef>
		<temperatureOffset>-60</temperatureOffset>
		<exclusiveConditions>
			<li>HeatWave</li>
			<li>NY_ForgingDragon_HotRain</li>
			<li>NY_ForgingDragon_Drought</li>
		</exclusiveConditions>
	</GameConditionDef>
</Defs>